title: Big Brother US Season 13 (FULL SEASON) [converted to mp4]

_______________________________________________

Big Brother US Season 13 (FULL SEASON)  

Same videos files, coverted to DivX

_______________________________________________

Windows Media Video 9  ---> DivX 

Original - low quality, this compression   
to DivX only effects megabye size, not  
the quality of the video/audio.

original .wmv  

Ep. 01-10 320x240

Original package size 13.8 GB

converted to .mp4  

Ep. 01-10 320x240

New package size 7.28 GB (6.52 GB smaller)
